<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">What are the best free AI tools for content creation?</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The strongest best free AI tools for content creation are ChatGPT&#8217;s free tier (GPT-4o with daily caps), Claude&#8217;s free Sonnet model, and Canva&#8217;s free plan with Magic Design and text-to-image included.</span></p>
